SEARCH

All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AuthToken
Authorization token to allow a user to access the database/use services
ClearRequest
request to clear database data
ClearResult
Result of request to clear database data includes response code of success(200) or error code includes error message if one is provided
CreateRequest
Request to create a game includes name of game to be created and authorization token
CreateResult
result of request to create a new game includes GameID of game created if successful includes response code of success(200) or error code includes error message if one is provided
DataAccessInterface
DataAccessInterface allows for data to be inserted and returned from the database Implementations for games, users, and authorization tokens
Database
Database Interface Stores Hashmaps of Games, Users, and AuthTokens in Hashmaps Allows the Data to be stored in a Database or in memory according to the implementation
Game
Stores data for a single game two users can play at once, one controlling white pieces, the other black each game has a custom GameID and name
JoinRequest
request to join a game includes Authorization token of user attempting to join and gameID of game to join allows color to be provided or not
JoinResult
result of attempt to join a game includes response code of success(200) or error code includes error message if one is provided
ListRequest
request for a list of games includes Authorization token of user making request
ListResult
result of request to list games includes response code of success(200) or error code includes error message if one is provided, otherwise includes list of games as message
LoginRequest
requests login of a user includes username and password of user requesting login
LoginResult
result of request to login user includes username and Authorization token of user includes response code of success(200) or error code includes error message if one is provided
LogoutRequest
request to logout user includes Authorization token of user
LogoutResult
result of request to logout includes response code of success(200) or error code includes error message if one is provided
RegisterRequest
registers new user in database includes username, password, and email of new user to be registered
RegisterResult
result of request to register new user includes username and authorization token of user registered includes response code of success(200) or error code includes error message if one is provided
Services
Services contains methods for all services offered by the API
User
Stores User data such as username, password, and email
